TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit RegistryArtifact extends System.Object

Docs.summary:
`Artifact` is the general term for items stored in a container registry, and can include Docker images or other Open Container Initiative (OCI) artifact types.
The class is a helper class that groups information and operations about an image or artifact in this container registry.
